comments: Jokic (DEN) splits his feet prior to the start of his dribble.
Jokic (DEN) turns slightly as he firms up in his screening position and he absorbs the side-to-side contact made with Wiggins (GSW).
Wiggins (GSW) clamps and holds Jokic's (DEN) left arm during rebounding, which affects Jokic's ability to cleanly retrieve the ball.
Correctly called 24 second violation on Denver.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in Gordon's (DEN) path and releases his hands away from Gordon's side as he turns to roll.
Curry (GSW) establishes a legal guarding position in Gordon's (DEN) path and absorbs the contact initiated by Gordon during the drive.
Barton (DEN) briefly has his arms around Thompson's (GSW) upper half before correcting.
Barton (DEN) closes out the jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Thompson's (GSW) right wrist after the release.
Jokic (DEN) firms up in his screening position in Thompson's (GSW) path and absorbs the contact.
Thompson (GSW) and Jokic (DEN) make incidental contact with each other reaching for the rebound.
Wiggins (GSW) engages and disengages with Gordon (DEN) during rebounding.
Gordon (DEN) moves forward toward Poole (GSW) in pursuit of the rebound and marginal body contact occurs with Poole as he secures the ball.
Wiggins (GSW) and Gordon (DEN) engage and disengage with one another as the pick is set.
Jokic (DEN) is moving alongside Curry's (GSW) path when marginal body contact occurs after Curry's gather.
Barton (DEN) and Curry (GSW) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.

After absorbing the initial body contact that occurs as Jokic (DEN) backs him down in the post, Green (GSW) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away before any incidental contact occurs to Jokic's front.
Morris (DEN) commits a take foul on Poole (GSW).
Poole (GSW) brushes Jokic's (DEN) back prior to making clean contact with the ball during rebounding. Any contact that occurs to Jokic's arm thereafter is deemed incidental.
Green (GSW) moves laterally and delivers body contact to Barton's (DEN) side, affecting Barton's SQBR during the drive.

Jokic (DEN) and Wiggins (GSW) come together at the same spot in the lane and, after the initial marginal body contact, Jokic makes clean contact with the ball prior to further incidental contact occurring with Wiggins during rebounding.

Thompson (GSW) brushes Barton's (DEN) left elbow and marginal contact occurs prior to the release of the put-back attempt. Green (GSW) brings his hand toward Barton's front simultaneously and marginal contact occurs as Barton releases the put-back attempt.
Gordon (DEN) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Iguodala (GSW) cleanly blocks Barton's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Morris (DEN) brings his left hand toward Thompson's (GSW) left side and marginal contact occurs as Thompson dribbles in transition.
Jokic (DEN) extends his left hand and makes clean contact with the ball prior to any incidental contact occurring with Thompson's (GSW) front.
